Google released its Year in Search.
Look what comes on top!

 

Even DeepSeek is on 6th place.
No ChatGPT this year.

headline: Google's Year in Search: Surprises in the Top 10
description: Explore Google's top searches of the year. Guess who's missing? ChatGPT! Even DeepSeek made it to 6th place. Find out what topped the list!
